description:
Yo peoples!

Tune in as Twon and Napoleon chop it up with the homie Nate Qwest. 

We discuss the kick off to college football (GO DAWGS) as well as Nate Qwest jounery as a music producer 

Make sure you share the podcast with your homies and let us know what you think on social media.
